text: Luis Enrique Palma Oseguera (born 17 January 2000) is a Honduran footballer who plays as a midfielder for Honduran club C.D.S. Vida.https://www.uslchampionship.com/luis-palma ==Club career== After two seasons in his native Honduras with Vida, Palma moved on loan to USL Championship side Real Monarchs on 12 February 2019.https://www.rsl.com/post/2019/02/12/real-monarchs-slc-acquires-luis- palma-loan-cds-vida ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Honduran footballers Category:C.D.S.
